A wise, mystical ewe stands in a forest clearing at twilight, her wool shimmering faintly with magical hues. Glowing runes and ancient talismans hang from her neck and curl in her fleece. Surrounding her, the background shifts with ethereal fragments suggesting enchantments, ghostly lands, and banished cards, while her clear, unyielding eyes hint at secret knowledge. The scene is straightforward but enchanting, with Baba as the undeniable focus, radiating legendary and elusive energy.